des:
Blaupunkt Technology products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.
After connecting Alexa to your Blaupunkt products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Blaupunkt Technology" app in android or iOS app market;
(2). Register one Tuya account in our "Blaupunkt Technology" app;
(3). You need to have a Blaupunkt device in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Blaupunkt Technology" app and change appropriate
name for your devices which will be used in "Blaupunkt Technology" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Blaupunkt Technology" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Blaupunkt Technology", and you'll be navigated to "Blaupunkt Technology" login page;
(9). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the plug.”
“Alexa, turn off the plug.”
